entries.journal_entry_description: Aja is too busy to handle all the patients herself. She needs you to heal the injured mechanic.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Use the bactapack on the mechanic who burned his hand. Look for him in the Medical Center.
entries.task00_journal_entry_title: Healing the Injured Mechanic in the Medical Center
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: You have helped the injured mechanic. Now return to Aja.
entries.task01_journal_entry_title: Return To Aja Sen in the Medical Center
